    <text id="B1157T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>How informs Bureau Headquarters of his intention to travel to Staunton, although
                    on what business is not known.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    Bureau of Refugees, Freedmen and Abandoned Lands,<lb/>Head Quarters, Sixth
                    District, Virginia,
                    <name type="recipient"><abbr expan="Colonel">Col.</abbr> O. Brown, <abbr
                            expan="Assistant Commissioner">Asstist Comr</abbr><lb/>Richmond, <abbr
                            expan="Virginia">Va</abbr></name>
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1865-12-21"><abbr expan="December">Dec</abbr> 21<hi
                                rend="super">st</hi> 1865</date>
                        <name type="place">Winchester, <abbr expan="Virginia">Va.</abbr>,</name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Colonel</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I have the honor to inform you that I find it necessary to
                    <unclear>proceed</unclear> through my District to Staunton, and leaving here
                    today I shall probably be absent until Saturday 30<hi rend="super">th</hi>
                    <abbr expan="December">Dec.</abbr></p>

                <p>As I expect to reach Staunton on the 23<hi rend="super">d</hi> and to leave that
                    place about the 27<hi rend="super">th</hi>, I desire that any communication
                    requiring my immediate attention may, if sent from Richmond between the 23<hi
                        rend="super">d</hi> and 26<hi rend="super">th</hi> of this month, be
                    forwarded to me at Staunton, <abbr expan="Virginia">Va</abbr>.</p>

                <p><abbr expan="Captain">Cap</abbr> Wells, <unclear>agent</unclear> accompanies me
                    to Harrisonburg where he will be temporarily stationed for the organization of
                    Sub-District "C".</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>I am Colonel<lb/>Very Respectfully<lb/>Your Obedient Servant</salute>
                    <signed>W. Storer How <abbr expan="Captain">Capt</abbr> &amp; <abbr
                            expan="Assistant Quartermaster">AQM</abbr><lb/><abbr
                            expan="Superintendent">Supt</abbr> Sixth <abbr expan="District">Dist.</abbr>
                        <abbr expan="Virginia">Va.</abbr></signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
